    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual VANOS variable valve timing. This chassis has been addressed with essential subframe reinforcement and a recent Rod Bearing service, ensuring the mechanical integrity of the 8,000 RPM powerplant. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, sending power through an M-Variable limited-slip differential. Suspension geometry remains true with updated poly-bushings for sharpened turn-in response. While the paint retains a deep luster, minor stone chips reflect its status as a dedicated performance machine rather than a garage queen. A mechanically sound example of BMW's finest naturally aspirated era.",
      "price": 34500.0,
